text: Mata-an! A Sukami na Inilahaman Nami Suka (Ya Muhammad), sa lagid o KĶiyailahami Ami ko Nuh go so manga Nabi ko Miyaoriyan Niyan: Go Inilahaman Nami so Ibrahim, go so Ismail, go so Ishaq, go so Yaqoub, go so Mbawata-an Niyan, go so Īsa, go so Ayyub, go so Yunus, go so Haroun, go so Sulaiman, go inibugai Ami ko Dawood so Zaboor
